Cranium
: Zygomatic plate broad, creating zygomatic notch (
character 28: state 1
). Posterior margin of zygomatic plate apparently situated anterior to alveolus of M1, but maxillary material fragmentary and broken in adult individuals so difficult to confirm (
character 28: state 0?
). Posterior margins of incisive foramina conspicuously projecting between procingula of M1 (
character 31: state 0
). Bony palate with shallow lateral longitudinally oriented troughs (
character 33: state 0
).

